# The wheel ships only the qsm_ci package (see [tool.setuptools] in pyproject.toml). With
# setuptools-scm installed, the sdist's default file finder would otherwise pull in the whole
# repo (algorithms/, web/, results/, data/ …) — prune the large, non-package trees.
prune algorithms
prune web
prune results
prune data
prune scripts
prune docs
prune .github
global-exclude *.nii *.nii.gz *.png *.pyc
include README.md CONTRACT.md LICENSE
